{"tid":1210872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"613 揸車小心隨時有油係馬路！！！要撘地鐵！！","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:05:57.000Z","uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1dc00717166aace3ffed02995af113eb00f78b","tid":1210872,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:35:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">啲暴徒會淋油落馬路！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要撘地鐵，否則隨時炒車，車毀人亡！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n封路清理路面油污<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1197693\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1197693</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［本報訊］石硤尾龍翔道昨午二時許發生漏油事件，長達二十米油迹遺留西行中線，警員需封鎖三條行車線由工人鋪上木糠「吸油」。警員在路旁撿獲一個壓至變形食油鐵罐，疑是罪魁禍首。事件擾攘一個半小時，工人趕及在下班時間前洗淨馬路，其間警方封閉龍翔道西行三條行車線，車龍延伸一公里。警方估計有運送食油貨車駛經上址，其中一罐食油跌下馬路遭車輛輾爆導致食油四溢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060316/5740722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060316%2F5740722&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=d7dd2b43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060316%2F5740722&h=03d6771a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060316/5740722</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請share 俾所有親戚朋友知！！"},{"pid":"c5a7261488fd8c97ded993dd698603e666e2e8bb","tid":1210872,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201afd65c3ef6dc099a1942a437aa0dcaac6f3a8","tid":1210872,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6ce63feadee5f851f9a56b509d2ad91db60a1a","tid":1210872,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4fb42f05d6d95c3a22b61c01c756a8187717a1","tid":1210872,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449dad7a9fce7f3c783c19fb7599daf4533df229","tid":1210872,"uid":198389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家高抬貴手 唔好阻我聽日返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}